---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-auto border-t border-gray-800 bg-gray-950 py-12">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
    <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Casino<span class="text-amber-400">Guide</span></p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          Comparatifs et avis indépendants des meilleurs casinos en ligne.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-300">Navigation</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/casinos/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-amber-400">Casinos</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-amber-400">Guides</a></li>
          <li><a href="/bonus/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-amber-400">Bonus</a></li>
          <li><a href="/comparatifs/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-amber-400">Comparatifs</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-300">Informations</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/a-propos/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-amber-400">A propos</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-amber-400">Contact</a></li>
          <li><a href="/mentions-legales/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-amber-400">Mentions legales</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-300">Jeu responsable</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
          Le jeu comporte des risques. Jouez de maniere responsable. 18+
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 border-t border-gray-800 pt-6 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
      &copy; {year} CasinoGuide. Tous droits reserves.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
